data.description: Come see this beautiful home ready for occupancy located in a non HOA small community of 12 homes and located 5 minutes to Naval Air Station Pensacola, 10 minutes to Cory Station and 10 minutes to the World's Whites Beaches located in Perdido Key, FL. This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath and 2 car garage is situated on the corner of the entrance to the development and is a great opportunity to purchase a home in paradise where you can work, shop and play. Scheduled your private showing today.
